<div class="crumbs"><a href="/index.html">Home</a> / <a href="/leagues.html">Leagues</a> / <span>Hoofdklasse · Netherlands</span></div>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-flag">Netherlands · Honkbal Hoofdklasse · 103rd Season</div>
    <div class="hero-country">
      <span class="hero-flag-emoji">🇳🇱</span>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-title">HOOFDKLASSE</div>
        <div class="hero-full">Honkbal Hoofdklasse · KNBSB</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-lede">
      The <strong>longest-running professional baseball league in Europe</strong>, founded 1922 — older than the MLB All-Star Game. Eight clubs, a top-flight known as "Honkbal" (literally "home-ball"), and a pipeline that has produced <strong>Jurickson Profar, Xander Bogaerts, Andruw Jones, Kenley Jansen, Didi Gregorius</strong>, and most of the Dutch WBC contingent that terrorized WBC 2009 and 2013. The Holland Series decides the Dutch champion every September.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div><div class="hs-num">8</div><div class="hs-lbl">Teams</div></div>
      <div><div class="hs-num">42</div><div class="hs-lbl">Games / Team</div></div>
      <div><div class="hs-num">1922</div><div class="hs-lbl">Founded</div></div>
      <div><div class="hs-num">UTC+2</div><div class="hs-lbl">CEST · ET +6</div></div>
      <div><div class="hs-num">103rd</div><div class="hs-lbl">Season</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page">

  <div class="watch-window">
    <div class="ww-title">⚡ When to Watch Hoofdklasse from the US</div>
    <div class="ww-lede">Netherlands is <strong>UTC+2 (CEST)</strong> in the summer — 6 hours ahead of US Eastern. Hoofdklasse games typically start at <strong>19:30 CEST = 1:30 PM ET</strong>. That's <strong>perfect lunch-hour baseball</strong> for US fans. Saturday afternoons and Sunday day games (14:00 CEST = 8:00 AM ET) are the weekend pattern.</div>
    <div class="ww-grid">
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">1:30 PM ET</div><div class="ww-lbl">Weeknight 19:30 CEST</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">8:00 AM ET</div><div class="ww-lbl">Sunday 14:00 CEST</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">10:30 AM PT</div><div class="ww-lbl">West Coast weeknight</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">Apr–Aug</div><div class="ww-lbl">Regular season</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">Sept</div><div class="ww-lbl">Holland Series</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">Sat 14:00</div><div class="ww-lbl">Best day window</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num">01</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Where to Watch Hoofdklasse</h2>
      <span class="section-sub">Verified Apr 2026</span>
    </div>
    <div class="platforms">

      <div class="platform-card premium">
        <div class="platform-tag">Primary · Per Club</div>
        <div class="platform-name">KNBSB · Federation Stream</div>
        <div class="platform-cost">Free / per-tournament</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          Dutch federation (KNBSB) operates streaming for top matchups, Holland Series, and European Champions Cup. Federation-level streaming; coverage varies by week. Check knbsb.nl schedule.
        </div>
        <a href="https://knbsb.nl" target="_blank" class="platform-link">knbsb.nl →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-card free">
        <div class="platform-tag tag-free">Free · Select</div>
        <div class="platform-name">Team YouTube Channels</div>
        <div class="platform-cost free">FREE</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          <strong>Neptunus</strong> and <strong>Curaçao Neptunus</strong> both maintain active YouTube channels streaming select home games free. L&D Amsterdam Pirates and Quick Amersfoort also upload content. Search team name + "honkbal".
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-card premium">
        <div class="platform-tag">International Events</div>
        <div class="platform-name">GameTime (WBSC)</div>
        <div class="platform-cost">Per-tournament pass</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          European Champions Cup (the continental club tournament featuring Hoofdklasse teams vs. Italian Serie A) streams on WBSC's GameTime platform.
        </div>
        <a href="https://gametime.sport" target="_blank" class="platform-link">gametime.sport →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-card premium">
        <div class="platform-tag">Domestic</div>
        <div class="platform-name">Ziggo Sport</div>
        <div class="platform-cost">Dutch cable</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          Ziggo carries select Holland Series and high-profile regular season broadcasts. Geoblocked outside the Netherlands.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-card premium">
        <div class="platform-tag">WBC Only</div>
        <div class="platform-name">FOX / FS1</div>
        <div class="platform-cost">Cable · WBC coverage</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          Team Netherlands' WBC 2026 games were carried on FOX in the US. Kingdom of the Netherlands roster included Jurickson Profar, Xander Bogaerts, and Didi Gregorius — mixed with Hoofdklasse vets.
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num">02</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">2026 Season Key Dates</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">Apr 17</div><div class="tl-title">Opening Weekend</div><div class="tl-desc">All 8 teams begin · 42-game regular season.</div></div>
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">May</div><div class="tl-title">European Champions Cup</div><div class="tl-desc">Top Hoofdklasse clubs face Italian Serie A and other continental opponents.</div></div>
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">Jul</div><div class="tl-title">Haarlem Baseball Week</div><div class="tl-desc">International tournament · national teams visit Pim Mulier Stadion.</div></div>
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">Aug</div><div class="tl-title">Regular Season Ends</div><div class="tl-desc">Top 4 teams advance to playoff round.</div></div>
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">Sept</div><div class="tl-title">Holland Series</div><div class="tl-desc">Best-of-7 championship · Dutch title at stake.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num">03</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">The 8 Teams</h2>
      <span class="section-sub">Hoofdklasse · 2026</span>
    </div>
    <div class="divisions-wrap">
      <div class="div-block">
        <div class="div-title">Hoofdklasse · 8 Clubs</div>
        <div class="div-teams">
          <div class="team-row"><strong>Neptunus Rotterdam</strong> — Rotterdam · Familiestadion · 2025 Defending Champs · Most titles (18)</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>Curaçao Neptunus</strong> — Rotterdam-based Curaçao affiliate · Perennial power</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>L&D Amsterdam Pirates</strong> — Amsterdam · 2024 Runner-up · Dutch royalty</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>Hoofddorp Pioniers</strong> — Hoofddorp · Near Schiphol · Longtime contender</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>Quick Amersfoort</strong> — Amersfoort · Utrecht region</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>HCAW</strong> — Bussum · Amsterdam region</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>UVV Baseball</strong> — Utrecht · University club · Returning force</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>DSS Kinheim</strong> — Haarlem · Host of Haarlem Baseball Week</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="did-you-know">
    <div class="dyk-badge">The Fact</div>
    <div class="dyk-title">The Hoofdklasse Pipeline Put Xander Bogaerts on the Field at Fenway</div>
    <div class="dyk-body">
      The Dutch-Caribbean baseball ecosystem is the <strong>most productive MLB pipeline on Earth outside Latin America and East Asia</strong>. Hoofdklasse and its Curaçao-affiliated feeder system have produced <strong>Xander Bogaerts, Jurickson Profar, Kenley Jansen, Didi Gregorius, Jonathan Schoop, Ozzie Albies, Andruw Jones</strong>, and dozens more. The reason: Curaçao and Aruba are part of the Kingdom of the Netherlands, which means Dutch youth development programs operate in the Caribbean with full funding and structure. A 14-year-old prospect in Willemstad is developed inside the same system that runs Hoofdklasse. Team Kingdom of the Netherlands has reached the WBC semifinals twice (2009, 2013) using this exact pipeline. <strong>When you watch a Neptunus Rotterdam game on a Saturday afternoon, you're watching the most efficient small-country scouting operation in baseball.</strong>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="watch-window neon">
    <div class="ww-title">⚡ Hoofdklasse This Week</div>
    <div class="ww-lede">See every Hoofdklasse game this week — times in NYC/ET, streaming links — in the <strong>Official Viewer's Guide</strong>.</div>
